Job Description:
The Caring Society offers exceptional undergraduate and graduate students paid internship opportunities at our Head office in Rawalpindi, Pakistan. Interns are matched with a specific department where they work on advancing critical projects. The overall aim of the program is to attract a pool of diverse, skilled, enthusiastic young professionals and provide them with an opportunity to build a long-term, substantive relationship with The Caring Society.Qualifications:Undergraduate student currently pursuing a degree in business, marketing, International Relations, communications, or other comparable fieldAbility to work in a fast paced environment with a demonstrated ability to accomplish multiple task and meet deadlinesAdvanced computer skills, including Microsoft Office Suite and strong internet search capability.
